features.name: Retweets
features.description: Retweet and undo Retweets, or retrieve users that have Retweeted a Tweet

features.name: Likes
features.description: Like and un-like Tweets, or retrieve a user's Likes, or a list of users that have liked a Tweet.

features.description: Hide or unhide replies to improve the quality of the conversation

features.name: Search Users
features.description: Search for Users, using advanced filtering tools to refine your search criteria.

features.name: Users lookup
features.description: Retrieve detailed, up-to-date information about a specific user, or users.

features.name: Follows
features.description: Follow or unfollow accounts, or retrieve an accounts followers or following.

features.name: Blocks
features.description: Block or unblock accounts, or retrieve a list of a user's blocked accounts

features.name: Mutes
features.description: Mute or unmute accounts, or retrieve a user's muted accounts

features.name: Spaces lookup
features.description: Retrieve detailed, up-to-date information about one or more Spaces.

features.name: Search Spaces
features.description: Discover Spaces based on keywords, and filter for results by status.

features.name: Direct Messages lookup
features.description: Retrieve DM conversation events, including new messages and when participants join and leave.

features.name: Manage Direct Messages
features.description: Create both one-to-one and group Direct Messages.

features.name: Lists lookup
features.description: Retrieve detailed, up-to-date information about a List, or the Lists a user owns.

features.name: Manage Lists
features.description: Create and delete Lists, or update List information

features.name: Lists Tweets lookup
features.description: Lookup Tweets for a specific list

features.name: List members
features.description: Add or remove List members. Look up the members of a List, or all the Lists a user is a member of.

features.name: List follows
features.description: Follow and unfollow Lists. Retrieve the followers of a List, or the Lists a user follows.

features.name: Pinned Lists
features.description: Pin and unpin Lists from your timeline, and look up pinned Lists

features.name: Bookmarks lookup
features.description: Retrieve the list of Bookmarks for a user

features.description: Create and delete Bookmarks for a user

features.name: Batch compliance
features.description: Keep your datasets in compliance by batch uploading and retrieving compliance statuses for Tweet and user IDs.

features.name: Usage
features.description: Retrieve information about how much data your project and apps have consumed.

features.name: Trends by woeid
features.description: The Trends lookup endpoint allow developers to get the Trends for a location, specified using the where-on-earth id (WOEID).

features.description: The Personalized Trends endpoint allows you to get personalized trends for an authenticating user account
